text: Narayana Panicker is the name of: *P. N. Panicker (Puthuvayil Narayana Panicker, 1909–1995), Indian librarian *Kavalam Narayana Panicker (1928–2016), Indian dramatist *P. K. Narayana Panicker (1930–2012), Indian religious leader *Narayana Panicker Kochupillai (born 1939), Indian doctor == See also == *K. N. Panikkar (born 1936), Indian historian
title: Narayana Panicker
